description.narrative: The overall project development objective is to increase access to modern energy in targeted rural areas and improve theplanning and management of sector resources by all energy sector institutions. Through its intervention, the project is expectedto contribute to improved reliability of electricity supply. Increased access to and reliability of electricity are key factors inthe realizationof the Government of Cameroon's (GOC) growth and poverty reduction strategy.
